data.description: Welcoming you to Winding Ridge is this very well maintained and updated 3 bd/  2bth ranch home. You will notice the covered front porch and professionally landscaped yard as you pull into the driveway. In the back yard you will appreciate the deck and privacy fence. As you walk into the front door you have neutral paint, steam cleaned carpet, large living room and kitchen with stainless appliances. Large master suite with a private bath and walk-in closet. This home also boasts a Brand New Roof!
